features.text:
Bad Bad Potatoes..
In the Station orbiting the Silly Planet, the potato harvest has started! During quality control, 3,333 defective potatoes were picked out by the hard-working Space Inmates.

Everyone is calling these potatoes the PixelTots, and they are going on a rampage! They’re running around stealing, and the latest reports say that they’re hiding and burning everyone's underwear, food, collectibles and more!

Catch these bad potatoes!!!

MINT YOUR NOW

www.pixeltots.com/
